---
const email = "jolmedo@outlook.com.ar";
const ubicacion = "Resistencia, Chaco, Argentina";
---

<section id="contacto" class="contacto">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-header">
      <h2 class="section-title">
        <span class="title-accent">@</span> Contacto
      </h2>
      <p class="section-subtitle">¿Necesitas contactarme? Aquí están mis datos</p>
    </div>
    
    <div class="contact-grid">
      <a href={`mailto:${email}`} class="contact-card">
        <div class="card-icon">
          <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
            <rect x="2" y="4" width="20" height="16" rx="2"></rect>
            <path d="M22 6L12 13L2 6"></path>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <div class="card-info">
          <span class="card-label">Email</span>
          <span class="card-value">{email}</span>
        </div>
        <div class="card-arrow">
          <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
            <path d="M5 12h14M12 5l7 7-7 7"/>
          </svg>
        </div>
      </a>
      
      <div class="contact-card">
        <div class="card-icon">
          <svg width="24" height="24" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
            <path d="M21 10c0 7-9 13-9 13s-9-6-9-13a9 9 0 0118 0z"></path>
            <circle cx="12" cy="10" r="3"></circle>
          </svg>
        </div>
        <div class="card-info">
          <span class="card-label">Ubicación</span>
          <span class="card-value">{ubicacion}</span>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    
    <div class="cta-box">
      <div class="cta-content">
        <h3>¿Tienes un proyecto en mente?</h3>
        <p>Estoy siempre abierto a discutir nuevas oportunidades y proyectos interesantes.</p>
      </div>
      <a href={`mailto:${email}`} class="btn-cta">
        <span>Enviar mensaje</span>
        <svg width="18" height="18" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2">
          <path d="M5 12h14M12 5l7 7-7 7"/>
        </svg>
      </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .contacto {
    background: var(--primary);
    position: relative;
  }

  .section-header {
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: 50px;
  }

  .section-title {
    font-size: 2.5rem;
    color: var(--text);
    margin-bottom: 12px;
  }

  .title-accent {
    color: var(--accent);
    font-family: 'JetBrains Mono', monospace;
  }

  .section-subtitle {
    color: var(--text-muted);
  }

  .contact-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(280px, 1fr));
    gap: 16px;
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto 40px;
  }

  .contact-card {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 16px;
    background: var(--surface);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 12px;
    padding: 20px;
    text-decoration: none;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
  }

  [data-theme="light"] .contact-card {
    box-shadow: 0 2px 12px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.06);
    border-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
  }

  .contact-card:not(a) {
    cursor: default;
  }

  a.contact-card:hover {
    border-color: rgba(0, 255, 170, 0.3);
    transform: translateY(-2px);
  }

  .card-icon {
    width: 48px;
    height: 48px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    background: rgba(0, 255, 170, 0.1);
    border-radius: 10px;
    color: var(--accent);
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .card-info {
    flex: 1;
    min-width: 0;
  }

  .card-label {
    display: block;
    font-size: 0.75rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
    text-transform: uppercase;
    letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    margin-bottom: 4px;
  }

  .card-value {
    color: var(--text);
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    word-break: break-all;
  }

  .card-arrow {
    color: var(--text-muted);
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
  }

  a.contact-card:hover .card-arrow {
    color: var(--accent);
    transform: translateX(4px);
  }

  .cta-box {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: space-between;
    background: var(--surface);
    border: 1px solid var(--border);
    border-radius: 16px;
    padding: 32px;
    max-width: 800px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
    gap: 24px;
  }

  [data-theme="light"] .cta-box {
    box-shadow: 0 2px 12px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.06);
    border-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.08);
  }

  .cta-content h3 {
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    color: var(--text);
    margin-bottom: 8px;
  }

  .cta-content p {
    color: var(--text-muted);
    font-size: 0.9rem;
  }

  .btn-cta {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: 10px;
    padding: 14px 24px;
    background: var(--accent);
    color: var(--primary);
    text-decoration: none;
    border-radius: 8px;
    font-weight: 600;
    transition: all 0.3s ease;
  }

  .btn-cta:hover {
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    box-shadow: 0 8px 30px rgba(0, 255, 170, 0.3);
  }

  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    .cta-box {
      flex-direction: column;
      text-align: center;
    }
  }
</style>